	(693,'_transient_dash_aa95765b5cc111c56d5993d476b1c2f0','<div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~3/KfjPkFLYrNc/\' title=\'Cell is a clean and lightweight theme. CyberChimps features Twitter Bootstrap, and responsive touch friendly theme options. Fotogram is a clean and fast loading theme. Spartan is a responsive magazine theme. Zenith is a responsive theme designed for blogs and magazines that aren’t about fluff. [&hellip;]\'>Weblog Tools Collection: WordPress Theme Releases for 1/6</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://ma.tt/2013/01/marshmallow-challenge/\' title=\'Here’s an interesting TED talk on a team challenge on building the tallest structure with twenty sticks of spaghetti and a marshmallow. See why kindergarten students do better than business school graduates. (Hint: Learning by shipping.) [&hellip;]\'>Matt: Marshmallow Challenge</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2013/01/04/ryan-green-child-theme-frameworks/\' title=\' [&hellip;]\'>WordPress.tv: Ryan Green: Child Theme Frameworks</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2013/01/04/michael-toppa-dependency-injection-for-wordpress-plugin-development/\' title=\' [&hellip;]\'>WordPress.tv: Michael Toppa: Dependency Injection for WordPress Plugin Development</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2013/01/04/john-housholder-the-future-of-wordpress-in-nashville/\' title=\' [&hellip;]\'>WordPress.tv: John Housholder: The Future of WordPress in Nashville</a></li></ul></div>','no'),
